### System Info API Tests
### Tests for SystemInfoController endpoints
### Uses {{baseUrl}} from http-client.env.json

### Get system health status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/system/health
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "Health should return 200");
  client.log("Health check passed");
%}

### Get available skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/system/skills
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "Skills should return 200");
  client.log("Skills count: " + response.body.length);
%}
